{"tid":2110064,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"公民黨未決定會否簽署確認書","createTime":"2020-07-15T15:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T15:30:53.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3adb22fc02e5dfac096a921bfa25893d99e0c6f6","tid":2110064,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>公民黨未決定立法會選舉參選人會否簽署確認書。</strong><br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋、譚文豪、鄭達鴻及郭家麒等公民黨成員，在民主派初選出線。公民黨指，會尊重初選結果，只派四人角逐直選選區，而落敗超級區議會初選的李予信則不會參加，又指公民黨未決定會否簽署確認書，會諮詢其他勝出初選的參選人尋求共識。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398102&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n34tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=2beb6e6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398102&h=b6741829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=398102</a>"}]}